title: ArtyTorrent Pack 46-Rock Drum Loops 100-109 bpm-WAV samples
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 46-Rock Drum Loops 100-109 bpm-WAV samples
-----------------------------------------------------------

I don&#039;t normally post anything that isn&#039;t obviously useful to dance music producers, but this pack contains some pretty funky loops. It&#039;s aimed at anyone who wants "live" acoustic drum loops for use in Rock and Pop productions, but it might also be useful to hip hoppers and people making big beat tracks.
Tempo ranges from 100-109 bpm.

Torrent contains 9 RAR files with 106 loops.
--------------------------------------------
Brian Daly Rock Beats 100-109 (9 loops)
Dave Abbruzzese Rock Drums 100-109 (6 loops)
Groove Master Rock 100 (15 loops)
MacDonald Rock (4 loops)
Misc Rock 100-109 (28 loops)
Pop Drums 100-101 (9 loops)
Siggi Baldersson Beats 100-109 (16 loops)
Studio Groove 100 (10 loops)
Velocity Drums 100-101 (9 loops)

All samples have been normalized and acidized and are 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz, looped precisely and containing the approx bpm in the filenames.

The samples are from a variety of sources including CDs produced by East-Weat, Syntrillium/Loopology and Sonic Foundry/Sony.

--
Arty - "Rockit"
10th February 2008.
